    "There are three cubes, each robot must place their cube on the correct target.",
    "There are three robots, each with a limited reach range, this means they can only firstly pick cubes from these panels, and then move or place these cubes on some appropriate middle coordination.",
    "Each task in Tool-RoCo can be formulated as a decentralized partially observable Markov decision process (Dec-POMDP) and a tool-selection process.",
